secondary_street_name: 28 Kirtling Street, 88 Kirtling Street and 2 Battersea Park Road
description: Non-material amendments to outline planning permission dated 23rd August 2011 (ref: 2009/3575) for restoration, extension, alterations and conversion of the Power Station building and demolition of other buildings and development of the land surrounding the Power Station to provide a mix of uses and open space and landscaping works. The non-material amendments comprise alterations to parameter plans for Phase 1, redistribution of hotel (C1) and assembly and leisure and non-residential institutions (D1/D2) floorspace between development zone RS-1 and RS-2, alteration to position of vehicular access to basement in RS-1 and new condition requiring development to be in line with circulation and access plans.
